<section class="we-planned py-5"> <div class="container-fluid"> <div class="container"> <div class="row align-items-center flex-md-row"> <div class="col-md-5"> <div class="yt-video-box p-3"> <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tFggZjPiLe0" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-7 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center mt-4 mt-md-0"> <h2>Why choose Vaidam Health to conduct medical camps?</h2> <p>Conducting a medical camp in international locations is NOT just about putting a doctor and patient in front of each other.That’s where Vaidam Health comes in !</p> <p>Vaidam proudly organizes medical camps across the globe, bringing esteemed doctors from renowned hospitals directly to communities in need. These camps offer a unique opportunity for patients to consult with top medical professionals in person, addressing their health concerns with expert guidance and care. By bridging the gap between patients and world-class healthcare, Vaidam ensures that quality medical advice is accessible to all, no matter where they are.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div>
